| 2024-06                     | Iseto Corporation                                                         | Kyoto     | Ransomware                 | 8Base               | 900 000 peoples affected by personal data exposition (name, addresse, vehicle license plate numbers, tax amounts and related documents). Tokushima Prefecture > 145 000 individuals affected (auto tax notices). Aichi Prefecture (Toyota) > 420 000 individuals compromised. | Iseto served multiple government bodies and corporate entities for sensitive tasks like tax notices and mail handling. A breach at this level can thus cascade into widespread exposure across multiple municipalities and large enterprises. | Nikkei Asia                                              | The 8Base ransomware group uses double-extortion methods, encrypting data and posting exfiltrated files on the dark web to pressure victims into ransom payments. This suggests Iseto likely faced both encryption and extortion demands. |
